'''Glascretia''' was one of the continental landmasses found on the planet [[Kamino/Legends|Kamino]]. It was the location of [[Derem City]] until the entire continent was submerged under some three [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] of [[Water/Legends|water]].

